Automation Queue

How to use the Automation Queue?
  • Facebook Group
  • Flowchart
  • Helpdesk Ticket
  • Lead
  • Message Template
  • Product
  • Podcast
  • Task
You can't use the Automation Queue because your Team Member account doesn't have permissions to access any social profiles.
Please contact the main account to grant your team account access to social profiles.

Account Timezone: Europe/Lisbon

2025-01-27 13:48:20
Attention:
  1. Please keep this page open and ensure that no power-saving settings are enabled on your device.
  2. Disable any pop-up blockers, as automations will be launched in new browser pop-up windows at the scheduled times.
  3. Before running your scheduled automations, ensure that you are logged into your social media profiles.
  4. You can run only one automation per social profile, so ensure it ends before scheduling the next one.
  5. If an automation is scheduled to start before the current one on the same social profile ends, it will be automatically rescheduled to begin once the running automation is complete.
